strings.Value: "Look around. What if someone is following us."
"You're always on the lookout for an attack! But just think about it: who in their right mind would follow a party including the invincible Ekun and a few of his insane friends?"
"All I do is look around. Everything is so different here, so unlike my homeland. Even the sky seems different!"
"Admirers, I suspect. They're hard to lose, even in this backwater!"
